data.name: Nutty Trail Mix
data.quickTastyDescription: A crunchy, energizing blend of nuts and dried fruits perfect for snacking on the go!
detailedCookingInstructions: Gather all ingredients in a large mixing bowl.
Mix the almonds, walnuts, pistachios, dried cranberries, sunflower seeds, and pumpkin seeds together until evenly combined.
Store in an airtight container for up to two weeks.
data.modifiersForBase: Include a variety of nuts and dried fruits for flavor and nutrition.
